-I ----ing hate a beach picnic.

17:55.367 --> 17:56.368
Let's double-time it.

17:56.409 --> 17:57.827
Hey, wait, wait, wait...

17:57.869 --> 18:00.330
Don't leave me,
Mathew's often alone.

18:00.372 --> 18:02.332
