18:12.676 --> 18:13.927
Amazeballs.

18:16.012 --> 18:17.931
Oh, my God, this
is way too heavy.

18:17.972 --> 18:20.517
I think I get
why people have these.

18:20.558 --> 18:22.310
I was having a God moment.

18:24.896 --> 18:27.440
[laughing]

18:29.943 --> 18:31.611
Wine glass to the left,
water to the right.

18:31.653 --> 18:33.530
Oh [bleep] it doesn't matter,
we need to go.

18:33.571 --> 18:34.698
Like, seriously.

18:34.739 --> 18:36.658
Just feeling blessed
in this moment.

18:36.700 --> 18:37.909
Are you doing a shot of tequila?

18:37.951 --> 18:39.786
-Would you like one?
-All right.

18:39.828 --> 18:41.705
Do you guys want me to
take a bottle of this over?

18:41.746 --> 18:43.039
-Yeah!
-Yeah.

18:43.081 --> 18:45.000
Bridge, bridge, that
is tender returning.

18:45.041 --> 18:47.335
All right, Katie,
Malia's on her way back.

18:47.377 --> 18:49.546
-Copy.
-To an amazing trip.

18:49.587 --> 18:50.672
Here we go.

