19:30.503 --> 19:32.422
Hasta luego.

19:32.464 --> 19:34.466
<i>Bridge, bridge,</i>
<i>that's tender returning.</i>

19:34.507 --> 19:36.468
-Nice work.
-Copy that.

19:36.509 --> 19:37.719
I'm gonna go
round up the guests.

