20:10.543 --> 20:11.503
-Wow.
-Wow!

20:11.544 --> 20:13.004
Spectacular.

20:14.589 --> 20:17.384
Ooh!
All right.

20:17.425 --> 20:19.010
Yeah, I've done a few
inspections in my time.

20:20.720 --> 20:22.389
Back to the grind.

